Here are the first three seasons of The Big Bang Theory TV series converted from AVI/XVID to Chromecast-compatible H264/AAC MP4 files.

To make it easier to play some of my favorite TV series on Google Chromecast, I decided to batch convert some of my favorite TV series AVI files to more robust and efficient H264 encoded MP4 files. This is much better than jumping through hoops using problem-prone &quot;transcoding&quot;. The converted files are 40% smaller without any noticeable loss in quality.

Video: H264 ( 624 x 352 ) -- Audio: AAC (m4a) 48000

